                    <div id="faq4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body faq-answer">
                            A: For saltwater use, we recommend flushing your engine after every ride to remove salt and debris. For freshwater, flushing once every few uses is typically sufficient.

                        </div>
